<span class="headers">Halas: Fang of the Wolf</span>
<p>
<p>
This quest originates with Ysanna Macgibbon in Halas. When you ask her "what gnoll fur" she reveals the following quest recipes:
</p>
<p>
Combine in any tailoring kit 4 <a href="http://eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1553&menustr=">Patch Of Gnoll Fur</a> to make a <a href="http://eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1552&menustr=">Gnoll Fur Patch</a>. (Trivial 21)<br>
Combine in any tailoring kit 4 <a href="http://eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1552&menustr=">Gnoll Fur Patch</a> to make a <a href="http://eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=5294&menustr=">Gnoll Fur Patch Quarter</a>. (Trivial 26)<br>
Combine in any tailoring kit 4 <a href="http://eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=5294&menustr=">Gnoll Fur Patch Quarter</a> to make a <a href="http://eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=5295&menustr=">Patched Gnoll Fur Bundle</a>. (Trivial 31&lt;x&lt;=33)
</p>
<p>
You can keep the <a href="http://eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=5295&menustr=">Patched Gnoll Fur Bundle</a> or return it to Ysanna for the Fang of the Wolf. 
</p>
<p>
Fang of the Wolf <br>
MAGIC ITEM <br>
Damage: 5 <br>
Delay: 26 <br>
Ratio: 5.2 Below Average <br>
Weight: 2.0 <br>
Weapon Skill: Piercing <br>
Classes: Warrior Rogue Shaman <br>
Races: Barbarian Vah Shir <br>
Inventory Slot: Either Melee <br>
Can be stored in Medium and larger containers <br>
</p></p><p>
